<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{#if title}}{{title}} — Microblog{{else}}Microblog{{/if}}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.css" />
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-white text-gray-900 antialiased">

  <!-- ===== SITE HEADER (logo + tagline) ===== -->
  <header class="border-b border-gray-100 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4">
      <!-- Sun / hope icon -->
      <a href="/" class="shrink-0" aria-label="Trang chủ">
        <svg class="w-14 h-14" viewBox="0 0 56 56" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="28" fill="#111827"/>
          <!-- sun rays -->
          <g stroke="#FBBF24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
            <line x1="28" y1="10" x2="28" y2="15"/>
            <line x1="28" y1="41" x2="28" y2="46"/>
            <line x1="10" y1="28" x2="15" y2="28"/>
            <line x1="41" y1="28" x2="46" y2="28"/>
            <line x1="15.5" y1="15.5" x2="19.1" y2="19.1"/>
            <line x1="36.9" y1="36.9" x2="40.5" y2="40.5"/>
            <line x1="40.5" y1="15.5" x2="36.9" y2="19.1"/>
            <line x1="19.1" y1="36.9" x2="15.5" y2="40.5"/>
          </g>
          <!-- sun core -->
          <circle cx="28" cy="28" r="7" fill="#FBBF24"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
        <a href="/" class="block">
          <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">Microblog</span>
          <span class="text-gray-400 mx-2">—</span>
          <span class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700">Chia sẻ kiến thức · Kết nối thành công</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          Nơi chia sẻ những kiến thức về lập trình, công nghệ và những góc nhìn cuộc sống mà tôi đã tổng hợp được.
          Hy vọng bạn sẽ tìm được những bài viết thích hợp để bổ sung vào kho tàng kiến thức cá nhân.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ===== NAVIGATION ===== -->
  {{> nav}}

  {{#if flashError}}
  <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-400 text-red-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm" role="alert">{{flashError}}</div>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if flashSuccess}}
  <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 text-green-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm" role="alert">{{flashSuccess}}</div>
  {{/if}}

  <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10">
    {{{body}}}
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-gray-100 mt-12 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 text-center text-xs text-gray-400">
      © {{currentYear}} Microblog · Built with NestJS &amp; Tailwind CSS
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
